DESCRIPTION:Do clearcutters dream of the sounds trees make as they are sa
 wed down in forests\, the same way I dream about the sound a tree might 
 make in a forest I’m not at all in? Flagging and Foraging explores mat
 erial ancestry and synthesis. All material comes from somewhere… like 
 old-growth...\nMore info: https://thevisualist.org/2026/04/izzy-davis-fl
 agging-and-foraging/\nVenue site: https://sites.saic.edu/sitegalleries/
